
=> APPLICATIONS OF STACK

    1) Function Call are implemented using stacks

    2) Checking for Balanced Parethesis

    3) Reversing Items (push items into the stack and pop them out, they will be reversed as stacks follow FILO/LIFO order)

    4) Infix to Prefix/Postfix conversion

    5) Evaluation of Prefix/Postfix expressions

    *******6) STOCK SPAN PROBLEM and its variations [MOST IMPORTANT STACK QUESTION IN INTERVIEWS]

    ***7) For implementing UNDO/REDO OR FORWARD/BACKWARD operations (as stacks follow FILO/LIFO order)  [ORAL STACK INTERVIEW QUESTION]
        Ex: How will you implement undo/redo operation in MS Word or any other editor?